{{Quote|The Coynite should no longer be a problem for us in the Dathomir system. Without their flagship they will have no staging point to continue their activities. You've completed your mission to the Emperor's satisfaction. Here is your duty pay.|Grand Inquisitor Ja'ce Yiaso|<ref name="SWG">''[[Star Wars Galaxies: Jump to Lightspeed]]''</ref>}}
[[Grand Inquisitor/Legends|Grand Inquisitor]] '''Ja'ce Yiaso''' was a [[Gender/Legends|male]] [[Zabrak/Legends|Zabrak]] [[Inquisitorius/Legends|Inquisitor]] who could be found inside the [[Emperor's Retreat/Legends|Emperor's Retreat]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. In [[1 ABY/Legends|1 ABY]], he had an [[Imperial Navy/Legends|Imperial Navy]] [[TIE pilot]] drive [[Coynite/Legends|Coynite]] [[Pirate/Legends|pirates]] out of the [[Dathomir system/Legends|Dathomir system]].

